Possible Fuel plugin tests:

* Install the plugin without the GroundWork installer being present in the /tmp directory.
* Install the plugin with an intact GroundWork installer present in the /tmp directory.
* Install the plugin with an intact GroundWork installer symlinked in the /tmp directory.
* Install the plugin with a corrupted GroundWork installer present in the /tmp directory.
* Install the plugin with a corrupted GroundWork installer symlinked in the /tmp directory.
* Deploy the plugin without a GroundWork installer in the installed software.
* Deploy the plugin with an intact GroundWork installer in the installed software.
* Deploy the plugin with a corrupted GroundWork installer in the installed software.
* Deploy the plugin on a node on which it is already deployed.
* Deploy the plugin on a node with insufficient resources to run it.
